<p><!-- intro section --></p>
<div class="container" style="margin-top: 20px;">
<div class="row">
<div class="col-md-12">
<p class="careers-section-header">Construct your career today with ConstructConnect</p>
<p class="body">Our team members are the heart of our business, and we’re proud of it. Whether it’s freshly popped popcorn at the end of the month, cupcakes to celebrate birthdays, early release on Friday’s to spend more time with the people who matter the most, or opportunities to volunteer with charitable organizations during the workday, we believe our work environment should be fun, collaborative, and engaging. We’d love to connect with you too.</p>
<hr/>
    </div>
</p></div>
<div class="row">
<div class="col-md-12">
<p class="careers-section-header">Who we are &amp; what we do</p>
<p class="body careers-section-subheader">OUR PROMISE</p>
<p class="body">ConstructConnect’s collaborative network empowers the construction industry to be more successful with access to relevant information through easy-to-use technology.</p>
<hr class="hr-invisible"/>
<p class="body careers-section-subheader">OUR MISSION</p>
<p class="body">We will connect the North American construction industry with the best information, technology solutions, and market relationships to drive our customers’ and investors’ success through a committed investment in the personal and professional growth of our talent.</p>
<hr class="hr-invisible"/>
<p class="body careers-section-subheader">OUR VISION</p>
<p class="body">We will transform the way the construction industry does business by providing our customers the information needed to drive their success.</p>
</p></div>
</p></div>
</div>
