<p><!-- benefits section --></p>
<div class="container" style="margin-top: 20px;">
<div class="row">
<div class="col-md-12">
<p class="careers-section-header">Our Benefits</p>
<p class="body">We value our employees and want to be sure that they know it too. That’s why we offer competitive benefits like a health and wellness program, 401K with company match, and paid volunteer hours. Learn more about the many benefits ConstructConnect offers below.</p>
<ul class="careers-ul">
<li class="careers-li">17 days of paid time off, 8 paid holidays, and 2 floating holidays</li>
<li class="careers-li">Leadership development opportunities</li>
<li class="careers-li">Individual career plans and opportunities throughout the United States and Canada</li>
<li class="careers-li">Health and wellness program</li>
<li class="careers-li">401K with company match</li>
<li class="careers-li">Medical, dental, and vision insurance</li>
<li class="careers-li">24 paid volunteer hours per year</li>
<li class="careers-li">Generous maternity/paternity leave</li>
<li class="careers-li">Fitness reimbursement program</li>
<li class="careers-li">Highly collaborative environment and passionate team members</li>
</ul>
<hr/>
    </div>
</p></div>
<div class="row">
<div class="col-md-12">
<p class="careers-section-header">Career Development</p>
</p></div>
</p></div>
<div class="row">
<div class="col-md-6">
<p class="body careers-section-subheader">Leadership Development Program</p>
<p class="body">At ConstructConnect, we believe that everyone is a leader, both at work and in their personal lives. We offer leadership development courses that allow people to grow confidently and position themselves for a successful future. Courses are offered regularly in person and online. As part of this program, we offer opportunities to take on projects or challenges with other teams in the business. We also offer a company-sponsored Toastmasters program.</p>
</p></div>
<div class="col-md-6">
<p class="body careers-section-subheader">Career Paths</p>
<p class="body">Whether you want to expand your responsibilities or grow your skillset, we are committed to providing an actionable career path for every team member. Each employee meets quarterly with his/her manager to set goals and objectives to advance their careers and develop a plan.</p>
</p></div>
</div>
<div class="row">
<div class="col-md-12">
<hr/>
    </div>
</p></div>
<div class="row">
<div class="col-md-12">
<p class="careers-section-header">Our Locations</p>
<p class="body">ConstructConnect is headquartered in Cincinnati, OH, but we have offices across the U.S. and Canada. </p>
